query:
SELECT 
  id, 
  name, 
  managerId,
  (SELECT name FROM employees m WHERE m.id = e.managerId) as managerName,
  gerencia,
  diretoria,
  active
FROM employees e
WHERE name LIKE '%Geane%' 
   OR name LIKE '%Rodrigo%' 
   OR name LIKE '%Mazuca%' 
   OR name LIKE '%Conselho%'
ORDER BY name;
